data.description: Stunning South Loop 10th floor condo! This condo has 10' ceilings with soaring glass windows and stunning panoramic views of the Chicago Skyline, Lake Michigan and Soldier Field. The unit includes quartz countertops, stainless refrigerator, stove and dishwasher, in-unit washer and dryer and custom cabinetry for additional storage. When entering the building you will find a large atrium entrance with a 24-hour door person for added security. ADDITIONAL STORAGE INCLUDED. PARKING AT $20,000.00. Short walk to the dog park, divvy bike located next to the building, centrally located to public transit, near great restaurants, walking distance to schools, the lake front, museums and aquarium. Mariano's only 2 blocks away. Also all residents have access to the 3rd floor terrace with grills!  Do not miss your opportunity to live in this beautiful unit in the heart of South Loop!
